rnet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aArchitecture. 4aArchitektur. 4aIT-Sicherheit. 4aautonome Systeme. 7aCOMPUTERS / Computer Science.2bisacsh1 aHeiß, Hans-Ulrich, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aJaeger, Michael C., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMühl, Gero, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWerner, Matthias, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Physical Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110637212oZDB-23-GPS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV  Informatik 2005-2012z9783110346794oZDB-42-OIN0 cprintz978348670414340uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348671088540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486710885423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486710885/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CHCOMSGSEN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GPSc2000d2014  aZDB-42-OINc2005d2012